# Rol Controller Tests

### Get All Roles
GET {{ComprasVentas_HostAddress}}/api/Rol
Accept: application/json

### Get Rol by Id
GET {{ComprasVentas_HostAddress}}/api/Rol/100
Accept: application/json

### Create Rol
POST {{ComprasVentas_HostAddress}}/api/Rol
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Administrador",
  "descripcion": "Rol con permisos administrativos",
  "permisoIds": [1, 2]
}

### Update Rol
PUT {{ComprasVentas_HostAddress}}/api/Rol/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Administrador Actualizado",
  "descripcion": "Rol actualizado",
  "permisoIds": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Delete Rol
DELETE {{ComprasVentas_HostAddress}}/api/Rol/1
Accept: application/json

### Get Usuario by Id
GET {{ComprasVentas_HostAddress}}/api/Usuario/1000
Accept: application/json

